t/uploads/2016/03/IMGL2681.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /><br />\nMakamu wa Rais, Mh. Samia Suluhu Hassan, akimkaribisha Ofisini kwake, Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi, Balozi Eng. John Kijazi, Ikulu Jijini Dar es salaam jana.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60764\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMGL2683.jpg\" alt=\"IMGL2683\" width=\"620\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMGL2683-300x182.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMGL2683-768x465.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMGL2683.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /><strong>Makamu wa Rais, Mh. Samia Suluhu Hassan, akifanya mazungumzo na Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi, Balozi Eng. John Kijazi, Ofisini kwake, Ikulu Jijini Dar es salaam jana, </strong><strong>Kushoto ni Katibu Mkuu Ikulu, Peter Ilomo.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PICHA NA IKULU.</strong></p>\n','<p>Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi, Balozi Eng. John Kijazi akifanya Mazungumzo na Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mstaafu, Balozi Ombeni Sefue, Ikulu Jijini Dar es salaam jana. Kushoto ni Katibu Mkuu Ikulu, Peter Ilomo. Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi, Balozi Eng. John Kijazi akikatibishwa Ofisini kwake na Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Mstaafu, Balozi Ombeni Sefue, Ikulu Jijini Dar es salaam jana. Katibu &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 12:06:49','2016-03-08 12:06:49','Kitaifa','Katibu Mkuu Kiongozi Akaribishwa Rasmi Ikulu','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('55','60775','post','nmb-yatoa-mafunzo-ya-kijasiriamali-kwa-wafanyabias','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/nmb-yatoa-mafunzo-ya-kijasiriamali-kwa-wafanyabiashara-nchini/','publish','NMB Yatoa Mafunzo Ya Kijasiriamali Kwa Wafanyabiashara Nchini','NMB Yatoa Mafunzo Ya Kijasiriamali Kwa Wafanyabiashara Nchini','<p><em><img class=\"size-full wp-image-60776 aligncenter\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"PIC 1\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-1-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-1-1-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-1-1.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Kaimu Afisa Mkuu wa Wateja Wadogo wa NMB &#8211; Abdulmajid Nsekela akiongea na wafanyabiashara kwenye hafla ya wajasiliamali ambao ni wateja wa NMB wa wilaya ya Kinondoni. NMB imekuwa ikuwakutanisha wafanyabiashara wakubwa na wadogo walio kwenye mtandao wa NMB Business Club kwaajili ya kuongea nao na kupokea maoni yao na mrejesho wa jinsi gani benki inaweza kuboresha huduma kwa wateja zaidi ya wajasiliamali 300 walihudhuria katika hafla iliyofanyika jijini Dar es Salaam. Mgeni rasmi alikuwa Mkuu wa Wilaya ya Kinondoni – Mh Paul Makonda.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60777\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"PIC 2\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-2-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-2-1.jpg 648w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Mkuu wa Wilaya wa Kinondoni Mh. Paul Makonda akiwa kwenye picha ya pamoja na washiriki wa hafla ya Business Club iliyofanyika Sinza jijini Dar es Salaam.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60778\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"PIC 3\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-3-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/PIC-3-1.jpg 648w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Meneja wa NMB Kanda ya Dar es Salaam &#8211; Vicky Bishubo akifafanua jambo kwa Mkuu wa Wilaya wa Kinondoni.</em></p>\n<p>Benki ya NMB PLC imetoa mafunzo ya kijasiriamali kwa zaidi ya wafanyabiashara 300 jijini Dar es Salaaam. NMB ina jumla ya vilabu vya biashara 34 nchi nzima vyenye wanachama zaidi ya 10,000. NMB Business Clubs zina malengo ya kuwafikia jamii ya wafanyabiashara wadogo, wa kati na wakubwa ambao wanajumuisha wafanyabiashara zaidi ya 50,000 ambao ni wateja wa NMB nchi nzima.</p>\n<p>Benki ya NMB PLC imekuwa kipaumbele kuhamasisha wanafanyabiashara nchini kujikimu kimaisha kwa kufungua vituo vya biashara nchini kimoja ambacho kipo kwenye wilaya ya Kinondoni- Sinza Business Centre. Vituo hivi sio sehemu tuu ya kuchukulia mikopo bali pia ni sehemu ya wafanyabiashara kupata ushauri kuhusu mikopo na biashara kutoka kwa wa wataalamu wetu.</p>\n<p>Kaimu Afisa wa Wateja Wadogo wa Benki ya NMB PLC alisisitiza kwamba lengo kuu  la vilabu hivi vya biashara vimeundwa  kuhakikisha wafanyabiashara nchini wanakuza mitaji yao, kuajiri watanzania wengi zaidi na pia kuchangia uchumi wa taifa hili kupitia ulipaji kodi.</p>\n<p>Akiongea na wafanyabiashara nchini Mkuu wa Wilaya wa Kinondoni Paul Makonda ameipongeza benki ya NMB kwa kuonyesha shauku ya kufanya mapinduzi ya kiuchumi kupitia vilabu vya biashara ambavyo vinawapa wananachi elimu ya kijasiriamali na hivyo kupiga hatua ya kuiuchumi kimaisha.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<p>Kaimu Afisa Mkuu wa Wateja Wadogo wa NMB &#8211; Abdulmajid Nsekela akiongea na wafanyabiashara kwenye hafla ya wajasiliamali ambao ni wateja wa NMB wa wilaya ya Kinondoni. NMB imekuwa ikuwakutanisha wafanyabiashara wakubwa na wadogo walio kwenye mtandao wa NMB Business Club kwaajili ya kuongea nao na kupokea maoni yao na mrejesho wa jinsi gani benki &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 12:06:52','2016-03-08 12:06:52','Kitaifa','Benki ya NMB','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('56','60784','post','kajala-tausi-na-asha-boko-ndani-ya-maisha-basement','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/kajala-tausi-na-asha-boko-ndani-ya-maisha-basement-kesho/','publish','Kajala, Tausi na Asha Boko ndani ya Maisha Basement Kesho','Kajala, Tausi na Asha Boko ndani ya Maisha Basement Kesho','<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60785\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/index-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"index\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/index-150x150.jpg 150w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/index-300x300.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/index-768x768.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/index-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/index.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n','','2016-03-08 13:07:45','2016-03-08 13:07:45','Burudani','','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('57','60801','post','serikali-yatoa-bei-elekezi-ya-sukari-kuwa-ni-sh-18','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/serikali-yatoa-bei-elekezi-ya-sukari-kuwa-ni-sh-1800-nchi-nzima/','publish','Serikali Yatoa Bei Elekezi ya Sukari kuwa ni Sh. 1800 Nchi Nzima','Serikali Yatoa Bei Elekezi ya Sukari kuwa ni Sh. 1800 Nchi Nzima','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60804\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"sukari\" width=\"620\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari-300x225.jpeg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari-768x576.jpeg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari.jpeg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /> <strong>Mkurugenzi  mkuu wa Bodi ya Sukari Tanzania, Henry Semwaza</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HATIMAYE  Serikali ya Awamu ya Tano chini ya Rais John Magufuli  imekisikia kilio cha muda mrefu  cha Wananchi ambao  walikuwa wakilalamika kupanda  kwa  bei ya sukari nchini.</p>\n<p>Akizungumza na Waandishi wa Habari  mchana huu  jijini Dar es Salaam Mkurugenzi  Mkuu wa Bodi ya Sukari Tanzania, Henry Semwaza amesema kuanzia sasa kilo moja ya  sukari itauzwa kwa sh.  1800 nchi nzima.<br />\n<i><br />\n&#8220;Serikali, kupitia bodi ya Sukari Tanzania, inawaarifu wananchi wote kuwa bei ya rejareja ya sukari sasa itakuwa sh. 1,800 kwa kilo moja</i>. &#8220;Amesema Semwaza na kuongeza;<br />\n<i><br />\n&#8221; Wafanyabiashara wote wanapaswa kuzingatia agizo hili, pamoja na kuhakikisha kuwa sukari inaendelea kusambazwa na kuuzwa kwa wananchi bila kuihodhi.</p>\n<p>&#8220;Maafisa biashara wa mikoa na wilaya watafuatilia na kusimamia utekelezaji wa agizo kuhusu bei elekezi ya sukari, na hawatasita kuchukua hatua stahiki za kisheria kwa wale watakaobainika kupandisha bei ya bidhaa hiyo. &#8220;</i></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>AGIZO LA SERIKALI KUHUSU BEI ELEKEZI YA SUKARI</strong><i><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60805\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari.jpg\" alt=\"sukari\" width=\"620\" height=\"913\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari-204x300.jpg 204w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/sukari.jpg 676w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></i></p>\n','<p>Mkurugenzi  mkuu wa Bodi ya Sukari Tanzania, Henry Semwaza HATIMAYE  Serikali ya Awamu ya Tano chini ya Rais John Magufuli  imekisikia kilio cha muda mrefu  cha Wananchi ambao  walikuwa wakilalamika kupanda  kwa  bei ya sukari nchini. Akizungumza na Waandishi wa Habari  mchana huu  jijini Dar es Salaam Mkurugenzi  Mkuu wa Bodi ya Sukari Tanzania, Henry &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 14:10:22','2016-03-08 14:10:22','Kitaifa','','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('58','60799','post','ilo-wanawake-bado-wanahangaika-kazini','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/ilo-wanawake-bado-wanahangaika-kazini/','publish','ILO: Wanawake bado wanahangaika kazini','ILO: Wanawake bado wanahangaika kazini','<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60811\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/cashew-ghana-jemima-1.jpg\" alt=\"cashew-ghana-jemima (1)\" width=\"540\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/cashew-ghana-jemima-1-300x201.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/cashew-ghana-jemima-1.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" /></p>\n<p>UTAFITI wa Shirika la Kazi Duniani (ILO) umeonesha hakuna hatua kubwa zilizopigwa katika kupunguza pengo kati ya wanawake na wanaume katika ajira duniani kwa miongo miwili iliyopita.<br />\nShirika hilo linasema pengo la ukosefu wa ajira kati ya wanawake na wanaume limepungua kwa asilimia 0.6 pekee tangu 1995.</p>\n<p>Katika nchi ambazo wanawake hupata kazi kwa urahisi, bado kuna tatizo la kiwango na ubora wa kazi hizo.<br />\nMatokeo hayo ya utafiti yametolewa huku ulimwengu ukiadhimisha Siku ya Wanawake Duniani.<br />\nMkuu wa ILO, Guy Ryder, akizindua ripoti hiyo ya utafiti, amesema hilo ni dhihirisho kwamba wanawake wanakabiliwa na changamoto kubwa katika kupata ajira.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60810\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/womenafricaworking.jpg\" alt=\"womenafricaworking\" width=\"620\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/womenafricaworking-300x225.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/womenafricaworking-768x576.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/womenafricaworking.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>&#8220;Katika umri wao wa kufanya kazi, wanawake wanaendelea kukumbana na matatizo katika kupata kazi nzuri,” shirika hilo la Umoja wa Mataifa limesema.</p>\n<p>&#8220;Ni hatua chache sana zilizopigwa tangu … 1995.”<br />\nRipoti hiyo ilitathmini takwimu kutoka nchi 178 na kugungua kwamba kiwango cha kushirikishwa kwa wanawake katika ajira ni 25.5% chini ya kiwango cha wanaume mwaka 2015, kiwango hicho kikiwa kimeimarika kwa 0.6% kutoka miaka 20 awali.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60809\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Rwandan-women-parliamentarians.jpg\" alt=\"Rwandan-women-parliamentarians\" width=\"620\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Rwandan-women-parliamentarians-300x180.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Rwandan-women-parliamentarians.jpg 620w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Ripoti hiyo inasema asilimia 6.2 ya wanawake hawana kazi duniani wakilinganishwa na asilimia 5.5 upande wa wanaume.</p>\n<p>Aidha wanawake wanaendelea kufanyishwa kazi saa nyingi kwa siku kwa jumla kuwashinda wanaume ukilinganisha na malipo kwa kazi iliyofanywa.<br />\nUrusi inaongoza duniani kwa kuwa na wanawake wengi wenye nyadhifa kuu, ikifuatwa na Ufilipino na Lithuania.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60808\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/154792022_3814ea92c8_z.jpg\" alt=\"154792022_3814ea92c8_z\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/154792022_3814ea92c8_z-300x208.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/154792022_3814ea92c8_z.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>Nchini Japan, ni 7% pekee ya nyadhifa kuu za uongozi ambazo zinashikiliwa na wanawake.<br />\nKuna pia tofauti kubwa katika biashara kati ya wanaume na wanawake.</p>\n<p>Ripoti hiyo inasema nchini Uganda na Tanzania, wanawake wengi wajasiriamali wamekuwa wakilalamikia gharama kubwa ya kusajili biashara na pia viwango vya juu vya ushuru kama moja ya sababu zinazowafanya kutosajili biashara zao.<br />\nKadhalika, jamaa zao wakiwemo waume zao na mashemeji huwashauri kutorasmisha biashara zao.</p>\n<p>CHANZO: BBC</p>\n','<p>UTAFITI wa Shirika la Kazi Duniani (ILO) umeonesha hakuna hatua kubwa zilizopigwa katika kupunguza pengo kati ya wanawake na wanaume katika ajira duniani kwa miongo miwili iliyopita. Shirika hilo linasema pengo la ukosefu wa ajira kati ya wanawake na wanaume limepungua kwa asilimia 0.6 pekee tangu 1995. Katika nchi ambazo wanawake hupata kazi kwa urahisi, &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 15:01:56','2016-03-08 15:12:54','Hadithi','Woman\'s Day','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('59','60814','post','maalim-seif-aweka-bayana-kuhusu-hali-ya-afya-yake','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/maalim-seif-aweka-bayana-kuhusu-hali-ya-afya-yake/','publish','Maalim Seif Aweka Bayana Kuhusu Hali ya Afya Yake','Maalim Seif Aweka Bayana Kuhusu Hali ya Afya Yake','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-60816\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/hi1.jpg\" alt=\"hi1\" width=\"668\" height=\"514\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/hi1-300x231.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/hi1-768x591.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/hi1.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" /> <strong>Makamu wa Kwanza wa Rais wa Zanzibar Mhe. Maalim Seif Sharif Hamad, akizungumza na waandishi wa habari katika hospitali ya Hindu Mandal Jijini Dar es Salaam kuelezea maendeleo ya afya yake.</strong><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-60817 size-full\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/hi2.jpg\" alt=\"hi2\" width=\"665\" height=\"900\" /><strong>Akiwapungia mkono kama ishara ya kuwaaga wanahabari na wananchi waliofika kumjulia hali.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Baada ya katibu Mkuu wa CUF <strong>Maalim Seif Sharif</strong>  kurejea kutoka India alipokuwa anafanyiwa upasuaji wa Mgongo na kwa mujibu wa Daktari wake upasuaji ulifanikiwa na aliporejea alikuwa na afya njema na akapumzika Zanzibar.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-reactid=\".1.1.0.0.2.1.0.0\"><span data-reactid=\".1.1.0.0.2.1.0.0.1\"><span data-reactid=\".1.1.0.0.2.1.0.0.1.1\">Leo March 8 2016 <strong>Maalim Seif Sharif </strong>amethibitisha jana hali yake ilibadilika ghafla akiwa uwanja wa ndege Zanzibar, alipata kizunguzungu kikali ikabidi asaidiwe kupelekwa kupanda ndege kutoka Zanzibar mpaka Dar es salaam na kisha kulazwa hospitali na leo ameyazungumza haya…</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&#8220;Nilipofikishwa hapa walikuwa washajitayarisha wamenipokea vizuri sana wakaanza kufanya uchunguzi wao na baada ya muda kama saa mbili tatu hali ikarudi ikatengamaa, nikalala salama usingizi mzuri na nimeamka salama asubuhi nimefanya mazoezi kwa miguu yangu mwenyewe na ninatembeatembea kwa miguu yangu mwenyewe, hali sasa hivi ni nzuri kama kama kawaida&#8221; alisema Maalim Seif Sharif  </em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daktari wa <strong>Maalim Seif Sharif, </strong> Omary Mohamed Suleiman amethibitisha pia kuwa afya ya kiongozi huyo kuwa ni njema na muda wowote madaktari watamruhusu..</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&#8220;Hakuna kubwa lililoonekana kila kitu kipo sawa, isipokuwa inaonekana ni hali ya uchovu alihitaji mapumziko zaidi na baada ya kufika hapa Hospitali madaktari baada ya uchunguzi wao wakaona bora abakie hospitalini wazidi kumuangalia mpaka kesho yaani leo mpaka sasa hivi hali imeenda vizuri tunategemea wakati wowote ataruhusiwwa kwa mujibu wa madaktari,&#8221; alisema Omary Mohamed Suleiman</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>(Picha na Salmin Said, OMKR)</strong></p>\n','<p>Makamu wa Kwanza wa Rais wa Zanzibar Mhe. Maalim Seif Sharif Hamad, akizungumza na waandishi wa habari katika hospitali ya Hindu Mandal Jijini Dar es Salaam kuelezea maendeleo ya afya yake.Akiwapungia mkono kama ishara ya kuwaaga wanahabari na wananchi waliofika kumjulia hali. Baada ya katibu Mkuu wa CUF Maalim Seif Sharif  kurejea kutoka India alipokuwa &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 15:45:01','2016-03-08 15:50:19','Kitaifa','','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('60','60807','post','shinda-nyumba-kwa-tsh-500-tu','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/shinda-nyumba-kwa-tsh-500-tu/','publish','Shinda Nyumba kwa Tsh 500 tu','Shinda Nyumba kwa Tsh 500 tu','<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60815\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/15-copy-1-745x1024.jpg\" alt=\"15 copy\" width=\"620\" height=\"852\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/15-copy-1-218x300.jpg 218w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/15-copy-1-768x1056.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/15-copy-1-745x1024.jpg 745w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/15-copy-1.jpg 990w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n','','2016-03-08 15:52:30','2016-03-08 15:55:56','Kimataifa','','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('61','60813','post','kim-tena-atupia-picha-nyingine-ya-utupu-mtandaoni','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/kim-tena-atupia-picha-nyingine-ya-utupu-mtandaoni/','publish','Kim tena, atupia picha nyingine ya utupu mtandaoni','Kim tena, atupia picha nyingine ya utupu mtandaoni','<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60825\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kim.jpg\" alt=\"kim\" width=\"620\" height=\"810\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Picha ya utupu aliyotupia Kim mtandaoni leo.</em></p>\n<p>Mwanamitindo Kim Kardashian amezua sintofahamu tena mitandaoni baada ya leo kutupia picha yake nyingine akiwa mtupu.</p>\n<p>Mrembo huyo ambaye ni mke wa mwanamuziki Kanye West ametupia picha hiyo ikiwa ni siku moja baada ya kuweka picha yake nyingine ya utupu katika akaunti yake ya Twitter na kushambuliwa na baadhi ya watu wakiwemo mastaa.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60824\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kim-monday.jpg\" alt=\"kim monday\" width=\"620\" height=\"705\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kim-monday-264x300.jpg 264w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kim-monday.jpg 634w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Picha ya utupu aliyotupia Kim mtandaoni jana.</em></p>\n<p>Picha aliyoweka leo Twitter inamuonyesha akiwa mtupu huku akiwa ameziba kwa mikono sehemu zake nyeti.</p>\n<p>Miongoni mwa mastaa walioiponda picha yake ya jana ni pamoja na komediani maarufu wa Marekani, Bette Midler (70) aliyeandika kuwa &#8216;Kim Kardashian ametweet picha ya utupu leo,. Kama anataka tuone baadhi ya sehemu zake ambazo hatujawahi kuziona, inabidi ameze kamera.&#8217;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60823\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Bette-Midler.jpg\" alt=\"Bette Midler\" width=\"634\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Bette-Midler-300x174.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Bette-Midler.jpg 634w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 634px) 100vw, 634px\" /></p>\n<p>Staa mwingine aliyempiga za chembe Kim ni mwanamitindo Chloe Moretz ambaye naye alimtaka Kim kuwa mfano bora kwa jamii.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60830\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Chloe-Moretz-1.jpg\" alt=\"Chloe Moretz (1)\" width=\"633\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Chloe-Moretz-1-300x152.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Chloe-Moretz-1.jpg 633w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 633px) 100vw, 633px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60832\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Chloe-Moretz-2.jpg\" alt=\"Chloe Moretz (2)\" width=\"620\" height=\"94\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Chloe-Moretz-2-300x45.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Chloe-Moretz-2.jpg 633w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n','<p>Picha ya utupu aliyotupia Kim mtandaoni leo. Mwanamitindo Kim Kardashian amezua sintofahamu tena mitandaoni baada ya leo kutupia picha yake nyingine akiwa mtupu. Mrembo huyo ambaye ni mke wa mwanamuziki Kanye West ametupia picha hiyo ikiwa ni siku moja baada ya kuweka picha yake nyingine ya utupu katika akaunti yake ya Twitter na kushambuliwa na &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 16:36:31','2016-03-08 16:56:43','Burudani','Kim Kardashian','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('62','60803','post','bahati-nasibu-ya-shinda-nyumba-yatikisa-mbezi','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/bahati-nasibu-ya-shinda-nyumba-yatikisa-mbezi/','publish','Bahati Nasibu Ya Shinda Nyumba Yatikisa Mbezi','Bahati Nasibu Ya Shinda Nyumba Yatikisa Mbezi','<p>WAKATI Bahati Nasibu ikiendelea kushika kasi, leo imeonekana kutikisa wakazi wa Mbezi ya Kimara na viunga vyake jijini Dar walionekana kuvutiwa nayo baada ya kujitokeza kwa wingi kuchangamkia magazeti ya Kampuni ya Global Publishers Ltd kwa kununua na kujaza kuponi kwa ajili ya kushiriki bahati nasibu hiyo.</p>\n<p>Mara baada ya maofisa wa Global Publishers kufika maeneo ya Mbezi ya Kimara wasomaji wa Gazeti la Uwazi walijitokeza na kununua gazeti hilo kisha kujaza kuponi zinazopatikana kwenye ukurasa wa pili wa gazeti hilo huku pia wakijipatia zawadi za kofia zenye nembo ya Shinda Nyumba zilizokuwa zikitolewa.</p>\n<p>Akizungumza na wakazi wa maeneo hayo Ofisa Masoko wa Global Publishers , Yohana Mkanda alisema: “Mnachotakiwa kufanya ni kununua magazeti ya Global na kujaza kuponi zinazopatikana ndani ya magazeti hayo ambayo ni Uwazi, Championi, Risasi Jumatano, Ijumaa Wikienda, Amani, Risasi Jumamosi na Ijumaa ambayo huuzwa kwa shilingi mia tano na msomaji anaweza kujishindia nyumba ya kisasa, kila anayejaza kuponi nyingi anajiongezea nafasi ya kujishindia nyumba hiyo iliyopo Salasala, Tegeta Dar na zawadi nyingine,” alisema Mkanda.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60836\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1-12.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1-12-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1-12.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><strong>Msomaji wa Gazeti la Uwazi aliyejitambulisha kwa jina moja la Philimon (kushoto) akijaza kuponi yake huku akipewa maelekezo kutoka kwa Ofisa Masoko wa Global, Yohana Mkanda.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60837\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2-9.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2-9-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2-9.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><strong>Mdau wa Gazeti la Uwazi, Alex Said (kulia) akisaidiwa kujaza kuponi yake na Ofisa masoko wa Global ili kushiriki Bahati Nasibu ya Shinda Nyumba.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60838\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/3-12.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/3-12-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/3-12.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><strong>Wasomaji wa Uwazi wa maeneo ya Mbezi Mwisho wakikata kuponi ili kushiriki Bahati Nasibu ya Shinda Nyumba .</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60839\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/4-7.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/4-7-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/4-7.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><strong>Ramadhani Mselemu (kushoto) akijaza kuponi yake ili kushiriki bahati nasibu hiyo.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60840\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/5-3.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/5-3-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/5-3.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /><strong>Kuponi zikiwekwa kwenye ndoo maalum ya bahati nasibu hiyo.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60843\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/6-3.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/6-3-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/6-3.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><strong>Amani Hamis (katikati) akijaza kuponi yake huku ofisa masoko wa Global, Yohana Mkanda (kulia) akifuatilia kwa makini zoezi hilo la kujaza.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60841\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/7-2.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/7-2-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/7-2.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /><strong>Khalid Rajab (kushoto) akijaza kuponi yake ili kushiriki Bahati Nasibu ya Shinda Nyumba.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-60842\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/8-1.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/8-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/8-1.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><strong>Wasomaji wa Gazeti la Uwazi walivyoonekana baada ya kumaliza kushiriki kujaza kuponi za bahati nasibu,ambapo walikuwa wakijisomea gazeti hilo.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Na Denis Mtima/Gpl</strong></p>\n','<p>WAKATI Bahati Nasibu ikiendelea kushika kasi, leo imeonekana kutikisa wakazi wa Mbezi ya Kimara na viunga vyake jijini Dar walionekana kuvutiwa nayo baada ya kujitokeza kwa wingi kuchangamkia magazeti ya Kampuni ya Global Publishers Ltd kwa kununua na kujaza kuponi kwa ajili ya kushiriki bahati nasibu hiyo. Mara baada ya maofisa wa Global Publishers kufika &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 17:40:55','2016-03-08 17:40:55','Kitaifa','Bahati Nasibu Ya Shinda Nyumba Yatikisa Mbezi','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('63','60858','post','wauguzi-wasitisha-huduma-butimba','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wauguzi-wasitisha-huduma-butimba/','publish','Wauguzi wasitisha huduma Butimba','Wauguzi wasitisha huduma Butimba','<p><strong><img class=\"wp-image-60859 aligncenter\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/MG_0197.jpg\" alt=\"_MG_0197\" width=\"627\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/MG_0197-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/MG_0197-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/MG_0197.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 627px) 100vw, 627px\" /> <img class=\"size-large wp-image-60860 aligncenter\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/baadhi-ya-wauguzi.jpg\" alt=\"baadhi ya wauguzi\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/baadhi-ya-wauguzi-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/baadhi-ya-wauguzi-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/baadhi-ya-wauguzi.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /> <img class=\"size-large wp-image-60861 aligncenter\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0200.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0200\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0200-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0200-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0200.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> Wauguzi, na madaktari wa Hospitali ya Wilaya ya Nyamagana Butimba mkoani Mwanza wakiendelea na mgomo jana.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60862\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0206.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0206\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0206-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0206-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0206.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60865\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02361.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0236(1)\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02361-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02361-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02361.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Wagonjwa wakiwa katika hali ya mshangao baada ya wauguzi, na madaktari kugoma.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60864\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0235.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0235\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0235-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0235-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_0235.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mkuu wa Wilaya ya Nyamagana, <span class=\"st\">Baraka Konisaga (katikati) akiongea na wagonjwa.</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60870\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/mkuu-wa-wilaya-akizungumza-na-wauguzi-pamoja-na-madaktari-wa-hospitali-hiyo.jpg\" alt=\"mkuu wa wilaya akizungumza na wauguzi pamoja na madaktari wa hospitali hiyo\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/mkuu-wa-wilaya-akizungumza-na-wauguzi-pamoja-na-madaktari-wa-hospitali-hiyo-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/mkuu-wa-wilaya-akizungumza-na-wauguzi-pamoja-na-madaktari-wa-hospitali-hiyo-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/mkuu-wa-wilaya-akizungumza-na-wauguzi-pamoja-na-madaktari-wa-hospitali-hiyo.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&#8230;Akiendelea kuongea.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60868\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02691.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0269(1)\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02691-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02691-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/IMG_02691.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60871\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ndugu-wa-wagonjwa-wakitafakari-hali-ilivyo.jpg\" alt=\"ndugu wa wagonjwa wakitafakari hali ilivyo\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ndugu-wa-wagonjwa-wakitafakari-hali-ilivyo-300x200.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ndugu-wa-wagonjwa-wakitafakari-hali-ilivyo-768x513.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ndugu-wa-wagonjwa-wakitafakari-hali-ilivyo.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />&#8230;Wagonjwa kabla ya mkuu wa wilaya kufika.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Na Idd Mumba, Mwanza</strong><br />\nHali ya usalama katika Hospitali ya Wilaya ya Nyamagana Butimba mkoani Mwanza kwa wauguzi, na madaktari sio nzuri na kusababisha wananchi kutopata huduma zaidi ya saa sita jana, jambo ambalo lilizua taharuki kubwa kwa wagonjwa na wananchi hospitalini hapo.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Mgojwa aliyejitambulisha kwa jina Janet John alisema wakifika katika hospitali hiyo ya saa moja asubuhi kwa ajili ya kupatiwa matibabu lakini hadi ilipofika saa tatu asubuhi hakukuwepo na daktari ama nesi aliyeingia katika vyumba vyao kwa ajili ya kupatiwa matibabu.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>‘’Sisi tumefika hapa hospitali mapema sana tukawa tumekaa kusubiri wauguzi na madaktari waje kwa ajili ya kutupa huduma lakini tuliona kila nesi ama daktari akija wanaenda kujikusanya sehemu moja tukadhani kuwa wana jambo lao wanajadili lakini ilipofika saa tatu asubuhi ilitubidi tukawaulize inakuaje mbona huduma hatupati ndipo wakatuambia hali ya usalama katika kazi yao siyo nzuri kwani kuna baadhi ya wagonjwa wanawatishia amani, ’’alisema Janet.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Baada ya kutokea kwa taharuki hiyo Mkuu wa Wilaya ya Nyamagana, Baraka Konisaga alifika katika hospitali hiyo na kuzungumza na wagonjwa pamoja na wauguzi ili kuweka mambo sawa ili huduma zianze kutolewa kama kawaida.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>‘’Kweli tumesikiliza pande zote kuhusiana na suala hili na hatupo hapa kwa ajili ya kupendelea mtu suala la kuhudumia wagonjwa ni wajibu wa kila muuguzi na daktari, wagonjwa ndiyo wateja wenu hivyo hali ya usalama tunalifanyia kazi na hakutatokea vurugu zozote.<br />\n“Mimi ndiye mkuu wa ulinzi na usalama hapa wilayani, nitahakikisha kuwa usalama unaimarika kila wakati ili mweze kufanya kazi yenu vizuri na wananchi wapate huduma zinazostahiki,” alisema Konisaga kisha huduma zikarejea.</p>\n','<p>Wauguzi, na madaktari wa Hospitali ya Wilaya ya Nyamagana Butimba mkoani Mwanza wakiendelea na mgomo jana. Wagonjwa wakiwa katika hali ya mshangao baada ya wauguzi, na madaktari kugoma. Mkuu wa Wilaya ya Nyamagana, Baraka Konisaga (katikati) akiongea na wagonjwa. &#8230;Akiendelea kuongea.  &#8230;Wagonjwa kabla ya mkuu wa wilaya kufika. Na Idd Mumba, Mwanza Hali ya usalama &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 18:21:35','2016-03-08 18:21:35','Kitaifa','Butimba','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('64','60874','post','jokate-atoa-msaada-kwa-kinamama-palestina','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/jokate-atoa-msaada-kwa-kinamama-palestina/','publish','Jokate Atoa Msaada Kwa Kinamama, Hospitali ya Palestina','Jokate Atoa Msaada Kwa Kinamama, Hospitali ya Palestina','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"wp-image-60875 aligncenter\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1-13.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"606\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1-13-300x225.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1-13-768x576.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1-13.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px\" /> <strong>Jokate akisaini kitabu cha wageni hospitalini hapo.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60876\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2-10.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2-10-225x300.jpg 225w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2-10.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" />Akitoa zawadi kwa mama aliyejifungua watoto mapacha.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60877\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/3-13.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"620\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/3-13-300x225.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/3-13-768x576.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/3-13.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />Jokate (kushoto)akiwa amempakata mtoto mchanga.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60878\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/4-8.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/4-8-225x300.jpg 225w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/4-8.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" />Jokate (aliyeshika maua) akiwa na kruu yake, chini ni maboksi ya zawadi alizopeleka hospitalini hapo.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-60879\" src=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/5-4.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"620\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/5-4-300x225.jpg 300w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/5-4-768x576.jpg 768w, http://globalpublishers.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/5-4.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />Mganga Mkuu wa Palestina, Dk. Kariamel Wandi (mwenye shati jeusi) akitoa shukrani kwa Jokate mbele ya waandishi wa habari.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ikiwa leo ni Siku ya Wanawake Duniani, mwanamitindo maarufu nchini, Jokate Mwegelo amesherehekea na kinamama wajawazito na waliojifungua katika Hospitali ya Palestina Sinza, Dar kwa kuwapa zawadi mbalimbali.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Akizungumza hospitalini hapo, Jokate alisema ameamua kusherehekea na wanawake hao kwa kuwapa zawadi mbalimbali kama vile viatu, dawa za meno kutoka kwenye kampuni yake ya Kidoti kwa sababu leo ni siku muhimu sana kwa wanawake wote duniani hivyo akaona siyo vyema kusherehekea peke yake.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">“Nina furaha sana kwa siku ya leo kwani ni muhimu kwetu sisi wanawake, nimeamua kugawana kidogo ninachopata kwa hawa wanawake waliojifungua leo na wanaosubiri kujifungua. Hii yote ni katika kuutambua umuhimu wa mwanamke duniani,” alisema Jokate.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>PICHA/STORI: GLADNESS MALYA/GPL</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<p>Jokate akisaini kitabu cha wageni hospitalini hapo. Akitoa zawadi kwa mama aliyejifungua watoto mapacha. Jokate (kushoto)akiwa amempakata mtoto mchanga. Jokate (aliyeshika maua) akiwa na kruu yake, chini ni maboksi ya zawadi alizopeleka hospitalini hapo. Mganga Mkuu wa Palestina, Dk. Kariamel Wandi (mwenye shati jeusi) akitoa shukrani kwa Jokate mbele ya waandishi wa habari. Ikiwa leo &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-08 18:30:29','2016-03-08 18:31:31','Kitaifa','','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('65','60918','post','huyu-naye-fuata-maelekezo-11','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/huyu-naye-fuata-maelekezo-11/','publish','Huyu Naye..!  Fuata Maelekezo-11','Huyu Naye..!  Fuata Maelekezo-11','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ILIPOISHIA GAZETI LA RISASI JUMAMOSI:<br />\n“Sawa baby wangu, nakupenda sana,” nilisema nikamwongezea na zaidi kisha nikasimama na kwenda kumpa denda, akalikubali, tukajikuta tukiganda humo kwa muda.<br />\nTuliganda tukashtuka baadaye, baba Rehema akasema&#8230;<br />\n“Umenikumbusha mbali, sasa unaweza kutoka humu ndani ukasingizia unakwenda saluni kuseti nywele?”<br />\nSHUKA NAYO&#8230;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">“Naweza, nitamwambia mama.”<br />\n“Umwambie, halafu ukishatoka unipigie simu haraka sana,” alisema baba Rehema akiondoka na kufunga mlango mkubwa.<br />\nNilikwenda kuoga, nilipotoka, kwenda chumbani kwangu nikakutana na mama akitoka huku akionekana kuwa na uso wa aibu, sikujua alifuata nini.<br />\nLakini nilipoingia chumbani na kukuta mazingira yakiwa vululuvululu ndiyo nikajua alikuwa akichangua vitu&#8230;<br />\n“Sasa hapa mama Rehema alikuwa akitafuta nini jamani?” nilijiuliza mwenyewe&#8230;<br />\n“Ahaa! Huyu alikuwa akitafuta simu yangu,” nilibaini mwenyewe moyoni. Kumbe mwenzake nilikwenda na simu bafuni kuoga kwani najua lazima mama atakuwa anaisaka ili aone nawasiliana na nani!<br />\nNikacheka kicheko cha kejeli tena kwa nguvu, huenda alinisikia kule alipo.<br />\nNilivaa, nikatoka, nikamkuta sebuleni lakini aliponiona aliangalia pembeni na hakuwa mkali kama ilivyo kawaida yake. Alijua nimebaini alichokifanya chumbani kwangu&#8230;<br />\n“Mama samahani, naomba uniruhusu niende saluni.”<br />\n“Wapi?” aliniuliza kwa mkato akiwa haniangalii&#8230;<br />\n“Popote pale.”<br />\n“Baba Rehema kaondoka?”<br />\n“Ndiyo.”<br />\n“Kasema anakwenda wapi?”<br />\n“Kazini.”<br />\n“Nenda uwahi kurudi,” aliniambia.<br />\nNiliondoka nikiwa na amani, maana sikukutana na ukuta wakati wa kuomba ruhusa hiyo.<br />\nNilipotoka getini tu, nikaanza kutembea kuelekea barabarani huku simu ikiwa sikioni&#8230;<br />\n“Haloo&#8230;nimeshatoka,” nilimwambia baba Rehema kwa njia ya simu.<br />\n“Oke&#8230;oke sasa sikia, tembea hadi kituoni, panda daladala uje kushuka kwenye kituo kinachofuata, kuna kibanda cha kuuza juisi hapo kituoni,” alinielekeza.<br />\n“Sawa.”<br />\nNilipanda daladala, nikaenda kushuka kituo alichoniambia baba Rehema, kwa pembeni nikamwona amekaa kwenye baa nikamfuata hapohapo&#8230;<br />\n“Karibu sweet,” alinikaribisha baba Rehema.<br />\nBaada ya kukaa, nikachezesha macho kuwaangalia wateja wengine pale baa, karibu wote walikuwa wakiniangalia mimi, sikujua kwa nini, maana si kwamba nilikuwa mdogo sana, halafu mimi nina umbo la kimamamama.<br />\nUkimwangalia baba Rehema na mimi huwezi kusema ni mtu na mtoto wake wa kumzaa&#8230;<br />\n“Mbona watu wananiangalia sana?” nilimuuliza baba Rehema nikijifuta jasho kwa kitambaa&#8230;<br />\n“We uko poa Jamila, unadhani ndani ya baa hii kuna mwanamke anakufikia kwa uzuri&#8230;. hakuna mi nakwambia,” baba Rehema aliniambia, nikacheka kwa mbali sana&#8230;<br />\n“<br />\nNikuhudumie nini?” mdada mmoja, alisimama pembeni yangu akiwa ameshika sinia na opena, nikajua baamedi.<br />\n“Soda&#8230;”<br />\n“Soda gani?”<br />\n“Kwani kuna soda gani?” nilimuuliza.<br />\nKabla hajajibu, baba Rehema ambaye alikuwa akituangalia, akadakia&#8230;<br />\n“Mpe bia huyu&#8230;”<br />\n“Aaah! Baba Rehema, bia tena?!”<br />\n“Moja tu tosha.”<br />\nNilimwangalia baamedi kwa macho ya kumwambia sawa lete bia&#8230;<br />\n“Bia gani?” akaniuliza baamedi&#8230;<br />\n“Yoyote&#8230;”<br />\n“He! Yoyote?” baamedi alishangaa, hata mimi nilishangaa&#8230;<br />\n“Ndiyo, yoyote!” baba Rehema alirudia&#8230;<br />\n“Haya, ya moto ya baridi?” baamedi aliuliza tena akitaka kuondoka.<br />\n“Yoyote!” baba Rehema alisema tena, baamedi akacheka huku akiondoka&#8230;<br />\n“Siwezi kulewa?” nilimuuliza baba Rehema nikiwa nakaa vizuri&#8230;<br />\n“Huwezi, kwani hujawahi kunywa?”<br />\n“Hata siku moja.”<br />\n“Kweli?”<br />\n“Kabisa&#8230;sijawahi kunywa. Lakini sidhani kama naweza kulewa. Kwani kawaida mtu analewa bia ngapi?”<br />\n“Wanasemaga saba, nane,” baba Rehema aliniambia, nikashangaa kwani yeye mwenyewe nilimkuta anakunywa bia, ina maana hajui analewaga ngapi?!<br />\n“Bia ilikuja, nikaifuta, nikaletewa nyingine, nikaifuta, nikaona silewi, nikaletewa nyingine, nikaifuta.<br />\nSasa kwenye kusimama kwenda chooni ndiyo nikajua ujinga wangu, nikayumba na kupiga mwereka puu! Baba Rehema akaniwahi&#8230;<br />\n“He! Jamila vipi tena?”<br />\nKumjibu nilishindwa kwani kila nilipotaka kuinua midomo, iligoma. Nilipofumbua macho nikahisi watu wote ninaowaona, waliokaa, walikuwa miguu juu kichwa chini na waliosimama pia hivyohivyo.<br />\nNilipoangalia mbele kwenye viti nikaona vinakuja kuniangukia kichwani, nikalala ili kukwepa visinifikie. Nilimsikia mtu mmoja akiuliza&#8230;<br />\n“Au amekunywa bia zenye sumu?”<br />\n“Hamna, huyu alisimama kunywa bia leo ndiyo ameanza tena,” alijibu baba Rehema, nikataka kusema muongo huyo, leo ndiyo mara ya kwanza, nikashindwa.<br />\nWengine walitoa ushauri nirudishwe nyumbani, hapo ndipo nilipokumbuka nitakachokwenda kutendewa na mama Rehema kwa kugeuza saluni kuwa baa&#8230;<br />\n“Jamila, tuondoke tafadhali,” alisema baba Rehema. Nikatingisha kichwa kukubaliana naye kisha akasema tena&#8230;<br />\n“<br />\nLakini wewe siwezi kukupeleka nyumbani moja kwa moja, lazima ukapumzike kwanza mahali, sawa?” pia nikamkubalia kwa kutingisha kichwa.<br />\nJe, unajua nini kiliendelea hapo? Usikose kusoma kwenye Gazeti la Risasi Jumamosi ijayo.</p>\n','<p>ILIPOISHIA GAZETI LA RISASI JUMAMOSI: “Sawa baby wangu, nakupenda sana,” nilisema nikamwongezea na zaidi kisha nikasimama na kwenda kumpa denda, akalikubali, tukajikuta tukiganda humo kwa muda. Tuliganda tukashtuka baadaye, baba Rehema akasema&#8230; “Umenikumbusha mbali, sasa unaweza kutoka humu ndani ukasingizia unakwenda saluni kuseti nywele?” SHUKA NAYO&#8230; “Naweza, nitamwambia mama.” “Umwambie, halafu ukishatoka unipigie simu haraka &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-09 05:23:54','2016-03-09 10:31:32','Mikasa','','Global Publishers')
INSERT INTO publishers_news VALUES('66','60932','post','jinsi-ya-kujijengea-heshima-kwenye-jamii','http://globalpublishers.co.tz/jinsi-ya-kujijengea-heshima-kwenye-jamii/','publish','Jinsi ya Kujijengea Heshima Kwenye Jamii','Jinsi ya Kujijengea Heshima Kwenye Jamii','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAKUNA kitu kibaya maishani kama kuonekana upo katika daraja la chini kuliko kawaida kwenye jamii unayoishi. Kisaikolojia kuna madhara makubwa.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kitaalamu hakuna jambo ambalo hutokea maishani bila sababu maalumu hivyo hata kudharauliwa kwako ndani ya jamii unayoishi kunatokana na jinsi unavyotenda mambo yako.<br />\nNinaposema hivyo ninamaanisha kuwa matendo yako, muonekano wako, kuzungumza kwako kunaweza kukufanya ukaonekana kituko na kushushwa daraja katika jamii.<br />\nMwalimu wangu wa somo la maisha na saikolojia, Eric Shigongo aliwahi kuniambia ‘Nothing happens in the sky, but the elements should be there’ akimaanisha kuwa hakuna kitokeacho angani pasipokuwa na dalili au sababu zake.<br />\nNaomba nianze kutoa njia za kukusaidia kurejesha heshima yako kwa kuperuzi na wewe baadhi ya dokezo muhimu zinazoweza kukusaidia kujenga heshima yako.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">MUONEKANO<br />\nKwanza kabisa ni jinsi unavyoonekana. Muonekano ninaouzungumzia hapa ni usafi wa mavazi na mwili kwa ujumla. Hata siku moja hakuna mchafu anayeheshimika katika jamii anayoishi hata kama ana kipaji kikubwa kiasi gani.<br />\nKwa hiyo uchafu wa mavazi na mwili huchangia mtu kudharauliwa katika jamii anayoishi. Linaweza kuwa jambo dogo sana lakini ni moja kati ya sababu kubwa inayochangia kuporomoka kwa thamani yako kwa watu.<br />\nMaana itafikia sehemu watu wanakwepa kuongozana na wewe kwa hofu ya kuaibika mtaani. “Tusiongozane naye atatutia aibu bure, mchafu sana bwana.”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">MAZUNGUMZO<br />\nHapa naomba nieleweke kuwa unachokizungumza kinaweza kukujengea heshima au kukubomolea. Kauli zisizo na busara zitakufanya udharaulike kwa kila mtu. Uropokaji usiokuwa na mantiki huchangia kuporomosha heshima yako hasa kama utakuwa muongeaji zaidi.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">UTENDAJI KAZI WAKO<br />\nNdugu zangu, siku zote heshima ya mtu ni kazi. Watu wengi hawapendi kufanya kazi kwa bidii huku wengine wakijiendekeza kwa tabia ya kuombaomba, jambo hilo halifai kwa vile huchangia kubomoa heshima yako mbele ya jamii.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">KUTOTIMIZA AHADI<br />\nKama una tabia za kuahidi mambo halafu unashindwa kuyatekeleza, basi unajiweka katika nafsi mbaya ya kutunza heshima yako katika jamii unayoishi. Bora ukwepe kutoa ahadi kuliko kuahidi na kutotimiza.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SIFA ZISIZO NA MAANA<br />\nNakumbuka msemo mmoja kutoka kwa mwandishi wa habari mwandamizi aliyekuwa muumini wa falsafa za maisha, Marehemu Adolf Balingilaki ambao unasema<br />\n‘Ukitafuta heshima kwa gharama ya juu, basi utalipwa dharau kwa bei nafuu.’<br />\nMsemo huu unamaanisha nini? Siku zote ukiwa unafanya mambo yako kwa ajili ya kusifiwa au mazungumzo yako kuwa ya ‘kujifagilia’ na kujiinua basi watu huishia kukudharau na kukuona mshamba wa maisha.<br />\nKwani hata katika maandiko matakatifu yanasema ajikwezaye hushushwa. Hivyo kujigamba na kujikweza kwako huchangia kwa kiwango kikubwa sana kuporomosha na kuondoa kabisa heshima yako hivyo kubaki mtu wa kudharauliwa tu.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">KUTOKUWA MWAMINIFU<br />\nSuala la uaminifu ni pana, kuna uaminifu wa fedha, siri, dhamana na mambo kama hayo, hivyo ni vema kila unachoaminiwa lazima ukitunze ukiwa mtu wa kuvunja uaminifu fahamu kuwa utashusha heshima yako.<br />\nKwa leo naomba niishie hapa, ukiwa na swali au maoni nitafute kwenye mtandao wa kijamii wa facebook au nitumie ujumbe kupitia namba za simu hapo juu.</p>\n','<p>HAKUNA kitu kibaya maishani kama kuonekana upo katika daraja la chini kuliko kawaida kwenye jamii unayoishi. Kisaikolojia kuna madhara makubwa. Kitaalamu hakuna jambo ambalo hutokea maishani bila sababu maalumu hivyo hata kudharauliwa kwako ndani ya jamii unayoishi kunatokana na jinsi unavyotenda mambo yako. Ninaposema hivyo ninamaanisha kuwa matendo yako, muonekano wako, kuzungumza kwako kunaweza kukufanya &#8230;</p>\n','2016-03-09 06:23:41','2016-03-09 10:33:15','Maisha','','Global Publishers')
